{"tid":1151132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰爆發】德國或漁人得利 德媒：出口預增$440億","createTime":"2019-05-12T11:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T12:17:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7066e5a647e64a8963130d866e92af5ebee651ea","tid":1151132,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T11:01:07.000Z","msg":"德國傳媒指，德國或成為中美貿易戰的得益者。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n美方指中國修改貿易談判協議內容，於上周五正式提高2,000億美元（約1.56萬億港元）中國商品關稅至25%。外界預期將對兩國經濟造成打擊。惟德國傳媒指，貿易戰卻增加德國出口。<br />\n<br />\n德新社報道說，德國基爾世界經濟學院認為，美中貿易衝突會讓德國漁人得利，給德國帶來很大的出口增長。因為，中美貿易衝突將限制中國對美國的出口，這會給德國企業帶來很多新的生意。由於德國企業寶馬在中國生產的汽車出口美國，令其會受到美國關稅打擊，但寶馬可能會把部份在中國的生意撤回到德國。德國整個國民經濟將得到推動，出口預計將增加50億歐元（約440億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n德國《南德意志報》指出，特朗普將美中貿易衝突升級至公開的貿易戰，其冷酷無情的談判方式可能會帶來對方的讓步，但這個勝利是短暫的。最大的失敗者將是美國的消費者，因為他們將為施加高額關稅的商品買單。<br />\n<br />\n有專家在德國《圖片報》上表示，特朗普發動貿易戰會給美國帶來輕微的好處，受到較大打擊的將是中國人。不過，貿易戰對世界經濟的影響則是毀滅性的。如果美中達成統一，這有可能給德國和歐洲帶來負面影響。但如果美中達不成統一，美中關稅的增長是肯定會給德國和歐洲經濟帶來負面影響的，因為經濟生產鏈已全球聯通。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190512/59591541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190512%2F59591541&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HahphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=c90da186\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190512%2F59591541&h=01ef11a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190512/59591541</a>"},{"pid":"61cd3cfbbaf7006ea6414399f596fd9aa7a9f644","tid":1151132,"uid":52194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T11:04:01.000Z","msg":"侵侵帶你發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171f18ebc08985b5ab7031cd25460f1372355851","tid":1151132,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"德國貨不嬲好過美國"},{"pid":"e85bc3b4b0cbfe5ca38ba4dadd9900ec5fce2f98","tid":1151132,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"中國製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n德國製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dba94e706cdd3e6c263a4d7633c153977c159f1","tid":1151132,"uid":234658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b484f3092613d647e4fe34137b2748a6101e41f","tid":1151132,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dba94e706cdd3e6c263a4d7633c153977c159f1","tid":1151132,"uid":234658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"全香港啲'小店' 都係淘寶野"},{"pid":"d0ef32bf4bbd70f765cce94c98d7fdb0ff772c5b","tid":1151132,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T11:16:23.000Z","msg":"德國或或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7df6379d692f25d7e0e66f81cead33039a571bc","tid":1151132,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"點只德<br />\n中美以外全部都有著數<br />\n東南亞印度 英法 全部應該都有賺<br />\n但西方國家應該賺得多過 發展中國家<br />\n變相美國送錢比歐洲 所以美國先搵歐洲開拖 回返水<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"8adc89a53971e4561b0d508d47d8f5181b4302d6","tid":1151132,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e647ca8e53a68c289dae